005package edu.wpi.first.math.kinematics;
006
007import static edu.wpi.first.units.Units.Meters;
008
009import edu.wpi.first.math.MathUtil;
010import edu.wpi.first.math.interpolation.Interpolatable;
011import edu.wpi.first.math.kinematics.proto.MecanumDriveWheelPositionsProto;
012import edu.wpi.first.math.kinematics.struct.MecanumDriveWheelPositionsStruct;
013import edu.wpi.first.units.Distance;
014import edu.wpi.first.units.Measure;
015import edu.wpi.first.util.protobuf.ProtobufSerializable;
016import edu.wpi.first.util.struct.StructSerializable;
017import java.util.Objects;
018
019/** Represents the wheel positions for a mecanum drive drivetrain. */
020public class MecanumDriveWheelPositions
021    implements Interpolatable<MecanumDriveWheelPositions>,
022        ProtobufSerializable,
023        StructSerializable {
024  /** Distance measured by the front left wheel. */
025  public double frontLeftMeters;
026
027  /** Distance measured by the front right wheel. */
028  public double frontRightMeters;
029
030  /** Distance measured by the rear left wheel. */
031  public double rearLeftMeters;
032
033  /** Distance measured by the rear right wheel. */
034  public double rearRightMeters;
035
036  /** MecanumDriveWheelPositions protobuf for serialization. */
037  public static final MecanumDriveWheelPositionsProto proto = new MecanumDriveWheelPositionsProto();
038
039  /** MecanumDriveWheelPositions struct for serialization. */
040  public static final MecanumDriveWheelPositionsStruct struct =
041      new MecanumDriveWheelPositionsStruct();
042
043  /** Constructs a MecanumDriveWheelPositions with zeros for all member fields. */
044  public MecanumDriveWheelPositions() {}
045
046  /**
047   * Constructs a MecanumDriveWheelPositions.
048   *
049   * @param frontLeftMeters Distance measured by the front left wheel.
050   * @param frontRightMeters Distance measured by the front right wheel.
051   * @param rearLeftMeters Distance measured by the rear left wheel.
052   * @param rearRightMeters Distance measured by the rear right wheel.
053   */
054  public MecanumDriveWheelPositions(
055      double frontLeftMeters,
056      double frontRightMeters,
057      double rearLeftMeters,
058      double rearRightMeters) {
059    this.frontLeftMeters = frontLeftMeters;
060    this.frontRightMeters = frontRightMeters;
061    this.rearLeftMeters = rearLeftMeters;
062    this.rearRightMeters = rearRightMeters;
063  }
064
065  /**
066   * Constructs a MecanumDriveWheelPositions.
067   *
068   * @param frontLeft Distance measured by the front left wheel.
069   * @param frontRight Distance measured by the front right wheel.
070   * @param rearLeft Distance measured by the rear left wheel.
071   * @param rearRight Distance measured by the rear right wheel.
072   */
073  public MecanumDriveWheelPositions(
074      Measure<Distance> frontLeft,
075      Measure<Distance> frontRight,
076      Measure<Distance> rearLeft,
077      Measure<Distance> rearRight) {
078    this(frontLeft.in(Meters), frontRight.in(Meters), rearLeft.in(Meters), rearRight.in(Meters));
079  }
080
081  @Override
082  public boolean equals(Object obj) {
083    return obj instanceof MecanumDriveWheelPositions other
084        && Math.abs(other.frontLeftMeters - frontLeftMeters) < 1E-9
085        && Math.abs(other.frontRightMeters - frontRightMeters) < 1E-9
086        && Math.abs(other.rearLeftMeters - rearLeftMeters) < 1E-9
087        && Math.abs(other.rearRightMeters - rearRightMeters) < 1E-9;
088  }
089
090  @Override
091  public int hashCode() {
092    return Objects.hash(frontLeftMeters, frontRightMeters, rearLeftMeters, rearRightMeters);
093  }
094
095  @Override
096  public String toString() {
097    return String.format(
098        "MecanumDriveWheelPositions(Front Left: %.2f m, Front Right: %.2f m, "
099            + "Rear Left: %.2f m, Rear Right: %.2f m)",
100        frontLeftMeters, frontRightMeters, rearLeftMeters, rearRightMeters);
101  }
102
103  @Override
104  public MecanumDriveWheelPositions interpolate(MecanumDriveWheelPositions endValue, double t) {
105    return new MecanumDriveWheelPositions(
106        MathUtil.interpolate(this.frontLeftMeters, endValue.frontLeftMeters, t),
107        MathUtil.interpolate(this.frontRightMeters, endValue.frontRightMeters, t),
108        MathUtil.interpolate(this.rearLeftMeters, endValue.rearLeftMeters, t),
109        MathUtil.interpolate(this.rearRightMeters, endValue.rearRightMeters, t));
110  }
111}
